{"tid":2258674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本土研究社發現新界兩年增逾800套丁丁屋 元朗最多","createTime":"2020-10-26T08:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T12:40:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b62a0010d230231a3d25570f1fcc711b5239649e","tid":2258674,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"本土研究社發現新界兩年增逾800套丁丁屋 元朗最多<br />\n<br />\n團體「本土研究社」發表新一份《新界套丁研究報告》，相對兩年多前發表的研究報告，發現新界新增超過800座疑似以套丁手法得來的丁屋。<br />\n<br />\n報告長達50頁，以網上衛星地圖等方式，研究新界不同地點，再翻查土地註冊處和公司註冊處資料，以及到現場考察等，找出三座或以上，建築風格相似及分佈一致，顯示透過以屋苑形式興建的懷疑丁屋屋苑，發現情況最嚴重是元朗區，有512座，佔總數超過6成，北區有113座，屯門有74座。報告又發現疑似套丁活動集中於新發展區周邊，認為可能與發展潛力有關。<br />\n<br />\n報告又提到，在個案分析中，首度發現有離岸公司疑似參與套丁，表示公眾難以查閱公司董事和股權結構，令人難以得知丁屋屋苑背後發展商的背景。報告建議，當局應訂立疑似套丁名單，而若有相當數量新丁屋屋苑正在興建，規模達十至數十座，應暫緩處理屋苑完工及轉讓申請程序，以作調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556716-20201026.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556716-20201026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=2fb2bde8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556716-20201026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e137d41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556716-20201026.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8eb4393441a0615b22b60d4927894e1e591a12e1","tid":2258674,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"元朗遙遙領先"},{"pid":"8d3a4ebf5557c5a3311bacec05532539bf93511f","tid":2258674,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"丁丁屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8269aeb7798177ca501886df2c699ab8039ef74e","tid":2258674,"uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"因為721要埋單？"},{"pid":"e6113b7d55f805c0abb71478d75251da5737dad3","tid":2258674,"uid":155077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"班鄉黑真係死不足惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d548a92055e821750a5c8ff7c6bd0ef2723ae7","tid":2258674,"uid":310587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"斬鄉黑丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1174e7b695d1e7aba69267b630f9acf45abcd8","tid":2258674,"uid":80413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啲鄉黑咁撚有錢"},{"pid":"7f2a9d9dbebc13ae08806f33b8f71839e3a94360","tid":2258674,"uid":139082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"800套 丁丁屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1673d8efd458eb3a3d97053b93535cedfbf89510","tid":2258674,"uid":80413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"地政做嘢未呀"},{"pid":"d7c5c3e41fe53ae52db5624d90cae47f656ccfbb","tid":2258674,"uid":92806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"離岸公司都有 cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}